<p></p>
<h1 id=3D"SD:MakerCheckerAuthorisationAuditLogs-Overview">Overview</h1>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">As part of the authorisation logs =
requirement, we are expected to capture the maker request details and all t=
he approval events as and when the checker approves the request. Also, as p=
art of the workflow request fulfilment process, if the underlying target Ex=
p API returns error/exception when PDP submits the request for processing a=
fter checker approval, the fulfilment error details event will have to be t=
riggered &amp; the details will have to be captured in the COSMIC along sid=
e authorisation audit log events.</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<h1 id=3D"SD:MakerCheckerAuthorisationAuditLogs-AuthorisationEventdetails">=
Authorisation Event details</h1>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">The following events will have to =
be triggered by Entitlements(PEP/PDP) as and when,</span></p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Maker requests are submitted</spa=
n></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Checker consent is submitted</spa=
n></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Workflow request authorisation is=
 completed(when workflow request reaches terminal state)</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Workflow request fulfilment fails=
 due to target Exp API error/exception</span></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
