<h2 id=3D"SD:MakerCheckerAuthorisationAuditLogs-ApprovalWorkflowAuthorisati=
onLogINFAPI">Approval Workflow Authorisation Log INF API</h2>
<p>A new INF API will be developed and exposed to retrieve the approval wor=
kflow authorisation log details from COSMIC DB. The INF will expose the fol=
lowing routes/end points,</p>
<ul>
<li>POST /approvalWorkflowAuthorisationLogs/summary &nbsp;=E2=86=92 This en=
dpoint/route will retrieve the basic approval workflow authorisation summar=
y info(like type, subType, requestGroup, createdBy and approvers list) for =
the supplied list of workflowIds or channelRequestIds&nbsp;=20
<ul>
<li>Request body to include list of workflowIds and list of channelRequestI=
ds. The consumers will have to supply either of the list to retrieve the au=
thorisation logs summary, sample request payload is as below.=20
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom">
<b class=3D"code-title"></b><span class=3D"collapse-source expand-control" =
style=3D"display:none;"><span class=3D"expand-control-icon icon">&nbsp;</sp=
an><span class=3D"expand-control-text">Expand source</span></span><span cla=
ss=3D"collapse-spinner-wrapper"></span>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl hide-toolbar">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Midnight; collapse: true" data-theme=3D"Midnig=
ht">{
    "approvalWorkflowIds": [
        "5b1dbb5e-fd44-49c8-b191-4c59d3633f5a"
    ],
    "channelRequestIds": [
        "WP765432"
    ]
}</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
<li>Response payload will include the summary of the workflow authorisation=
 logs for the supplied workflowIds or channelRequestIds, sample response pa=
yload is as below.=20
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom">
<b class=3D"code-title"></b><span class=3D"collapse-source expand-control" =
style=3D"display:none;"><span class=3D"expand-control-icon icon">&nbsp;</sp=
an><span class=3D"expand-control-text">Expand source</span></span><span cla=
ss=3D"collapse-spinner-wrapper"></span>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl hide-toolbar">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Midnight; collapse: true" data-theme=3D"Midnig=
ht">{
    "data": {
        "approvalWorkflowAuthorisationLogSummary": [
            {
                "approvalWorkflowId": "5b1dbb5e-fd44-49c8-b191-4c59d3633f5a=
",
                "approvalChannel": "W1C-Customer",
                "type": "w1cpayments",
                "subType": "payments",
                "workflowStatusUpdates": [
                    {
                        "status": "ApprovalPending",
                        "auditLogCreatedDateTime": "2025-09-10T14:15:22Z"
                    },
                    {
                        "status": "Approved",
                        "auditLogCreatedDateTime": "2025-09-11T16:15:22Z"
                    }
                ],
                "authorisationModel": "SingleAuth",
                "workflowRequestCreatedBy": {
                    "id": "123456789",
                    "idScheme": "CustomerInternalId",
                    "firstName": "John",
                    "lastName": "Smith"
                },
                "approvers": [
                    {
                        "userId": "987654321",
                        "userIdScheme": "CustomerInternalId",
                        "firstName": "Simon",
                        "lastName": "Young",
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbs=
p; &nbsp;"auditLogCreatedDateTime": "2025-09-10T14:15:22Z"
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; },
                    {
                        "userId": "987654323",
                        "userIdScheme": "CustomerInternalId",
                        "firstName": "David",
                        "lastName": "Wood",
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbs=
p; &nbsp;"auditLogCreatedDateTime": "2025-09-10T14:15:22Z"
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }
                ],
                "actionedBy": [
                    {
                        "userId": "987654321",
                        "userIdScheme": "CustomerInternalId",
                        "status": "Approved",
                        "firstName": "Simon",
                        "lastName": "Young",
                        "capturedDateTime": "2025-09-11T16:15:22Z",
                        "notes": "string",
                        "auditLogCreatedDateTime": "2025-09-11T16:16:22Z"
                    }
                ],
                "workflowRequestCreatedDateTime": "2025-09-10T14:15:22Z",
                "requestGroup": "Customer",
                "channelRequestId": "WP765432",
                "auditLogCreatedDateTime": "2025-09-10T14:17:22Z"
            }
        ]
    }
}</pre>
</div>
</div><p><br></p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>GET /approvalWorkflowAuthorisationLogs/details =E2=86=92 This endpoint/=
route will retrieve the approval workflow details for the supplied workflow=
Id or channelRequestId=20
<ul>
<li>This endpoint/route will accept either of the following query string pa=
rameters=20
<ul>
<li>workflowId=3D{workflowId}&nbsp;</li>
<li>channelRequestId =3D {channelRequestId}</li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p>Response payload will include the details of the workflow authorisation =
log for the supplied workflowId or channelRequestId, sample response payloa=
d is as below.</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom">
<b class=3D"code-title"></b><span class=3D"collapse-source expand-control" =
style=3D"display:none;"><span class=3D"expand-control-icon icon">&nbsp;</sp=
an><span class=3D"expand-control-text">Expand source</span></span><span cla=
ss=3D"collapse-spinner-wrapper"></span>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl hide-toolbar">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Midnight; collapse: true" data-theme=3D"Midnig=
ht">{
