<h2 id=3D"SD:MakerCheckerAuthorisationAuditLogs-ApprovalWorkflowAuthorisati=
onLogEXPAPI">Approval Workflow Authorisation Log EXP API</h2>
<p>New endpoints will be developed and exposed from <strong>galaxy-maker-ch=
ecker-widget-exp</strong> API to retrieve the approval workflow authorisati=
on log details. Following routes/end points will be exposed to meet to the =
channels requirements,</p>
<ul>
<li>Get authorisation log summary : <a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westp=
ac.com.au/display/ARTC/galaxy-maker-checker-widget-exp-v1#galaxymakerchecke=
rwidgetexpv1-GET/authorisationSummary" rel=3D"nofollow">galaxymakercheckerw=
idgetexpv1-GET/authorisationSummary</a></li>
<li>Get authorisation log details: <a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpa=
c.com.au/display/ARTC/galaxy-maker-checker-widget-exp-v1#galaxymakerchecker=
widgetexpv1-GET/authorisationDetail" rel=3D"nofollow">galaxymakercheckerwid=
getexpv1-GET/authorisationDetail</a></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
